<abstract>
This manual covers the use of <bf>mpd</bf> version <bf>&version;</bf>,
a multi-link PPP daemon for FreeBSD based on <tt>netgraph(4)</tt>.

You must be running FreeBSD version 5.x or higher to use it, and
it is advised to have the latest system version to get access to
all mpd features.
</abstract>

